simple concurrency primitives inspired by
goroutines and the javascript event loop

           ⢰⣿⣿⣿⣆⣀    ⢠ ⡘ ⡄    
         ⠰⠞⢻⣿⣿⣿⡏⠉⠉  ⢀⣾⣠⡇⣸⠃    
         ⢀⣤⣌⣿⣿⡿⠁    ⠈⠉⣿⡟⠿     
        ⣠⣾⠿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣶⣄  ⣠⣾⣿⠃      
      ⠠⣾⣿⡃ ⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠙⢿⣷⣾⡿⣻⡇       
       ⠈⠛⢿⣶⣿⣿⣿⣿⡿  ⠉⠁ ⣿⠁       
          ⠉⣿⣿⣿⣿⡇    ⢸⡏        
          ⢠⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷    ⣾⠃        
          ⢸⣿⣿⢻⣿⣿⡆  ⢰⡿         
          ⣿⣿⡏ ⣿⣿⣷  ⣼⡇         
         ⢀⣿⣿⠁ ⠸⣿⣿⡄ ⣿          
         ⢸⣿⡟   ⢿⣿⣧⢠⡏          
         ⣾⣿⠃   ⠘⣿⣿⣾⠃          
         ⠉⠉     ⠉⠉            

usage:

```
scons run        # build and run the main binary
scons test       # build and run all tests
scons valgrind   # build and run the main binary under a memcheck

scons fmt        # format all source files with clang-format
scons --clean    # clean all build artifacts
```
